    "category": ["action", "leadership"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated", "brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q068",
    "text": "A smooth sea never made a skilled sailor.",
    "author": "Franklin D. Roosevelt",
    "category": ["endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave", "uncertain"],
    "season_tags": ["winter"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q069",
    "text": "I have not failed. I've just found 10,000 ways that won't work.",
    "author": "Thomas Edison",
    "category": ["endurance", "discipline"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "uncertain"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q070",
    "text": "Everything you've ever wanted is on the other side of fear.",
    "author": "George Addair",
    "category": ["action", "endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave", "uncertain"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q071",
    "text": "勝ちに不思議の勝ちあり、負けに不思議の負けなし。",
    "author": "野村克也",
    "category": ["discipline", "reflection"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q072",
    "text": "The greatest glory in living lies not in never falling, but in rising every time we fall.",
    "author": "Nelson Mandela",
    "category": ["endurance", "leadership"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q073",
    "text": "Happiness is not something ready made. It comes from your own actions.",
    "author": "Dalai Lama",
    "category": ["action", "gratitude"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["uncertain"],
    "season_tags": ["spring"],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q074",
    "text": "千里の道も一歩から。",
    "author": "老子",
    "category": ["action", "endurance"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": ["uncertain"],
    "season_tags": ["spring"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q075",
    "text": "The best revenge is massive success.",
    "author": "Frank Sinatra",
    "category": ["action", "endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave", "motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q076",
    "text": "Your time is limited. Don't waste it living someone else's life.",
    "author": "Steve Jobs",
    "category": ["action", "reflection"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q077",
    "text": "Do not go where the path may lead; go instead where there is no path and leave a trail.",
    "author": "Ralph Waldo Emerson",
    "category": ["leadership", "action"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q078",
    "text": "The wound is the place where the Light enters you.",
    "author": "Rumi",
    "category": ["reflection", "endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["uncertain", "tired"],
    "season_tags": ["winter"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q079",
    "text": "七転び八起き。",
    "author": "",
    "category": ["endurance", "discipline"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q080",
    "text": "The two most important days in your life are the day you are born and the day you find out why.",
    "author": "Mark Twain",
    "category": ["reflection", "leadership"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["uncertain"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q081",
    "text": "Difficult roads often lead to beautiful destinations.",
    "author": "",
    "category": ["endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "original",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "uncertain"],
    "season_tags": ["winter"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q082",
    "text": "In three words I can sum up everything I've learned about life: it goes on.",
    "author": "Robert Frost",
    "category": ["reflection", "endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "stressed"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q083",
    "text": "継続は力なり。",
    "author": "",
    "category": ["discipline", "endurance"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q084",
    "text": "First they ignore you, then they ridicule you, then they fight you, and then you win.",
    "author": "Mahatma Gandhi",
    "category": ["endurance", "leadership"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q085",
    "text": "Don't count the days. Make the days count.",
    "author": "Muhammad Ali",
    "category": ["action", "discipline"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q086",
    "text": "人生に失敗がないと、人生を失敗する。",
    "author": "斎藤茂太",
    "category": ["reflection", "endurance"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": ["uncertain"],
    "season_tags": ["autumn"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q087",
    "text": "The only person you are destined to become is the person you decide to be.",
    "author": "Ralph Waldo Emerson",
    "category": ["action", "leadership"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave", "motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q088",
    "text": "What we achieve inwardly will change outer reality.",
    "author": "Plutarch",
    "category": ["reflection", "focus"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": [],
    "season_tags": ["autumn"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q089",
    "text": "Fall seven times, stand up eight.",
    "author": "",
    "category": ["endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "original",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q090",
    "text": "為せば成る、為さねば成らぬ何事も。",
    "author": "上杉鷹山",
    "category": ["action", "discipline"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q091",
    "text": "Innovation distinguishes between a leader and a follower.",
    "author": "Steve Jobs",
    "category": ["leadership", "action"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q092",
    "text": "The only true wisdom is in knowing you know nothing.",
    "author": "Socrates",
    "category": ["reflection"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": [],
    "season_tags": ["autumn"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q093",
    "text": "When you reach the end of your rope, tie a knot in it and hang on.",
    "author": "Franklin D. Roosevelt",
    "category": ["endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "stressed"],
    "season_tags": ["winter"],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q094",
    "text": "情けは人の為ならず。",
    "author": "",
    "category": ["gratitude", "leadership"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": [],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q095",
    "text": "Start where you are. Use what you have. Do what you can.",
    "author": "Arthur Ashe",
    "category": ["action", "endurance"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["uncertain", "tired"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q096",
    "text": "Sow a thought, reap an action. Sow an action, reap a habit.",
    "author": "Stephen Covey",
    "category": ["discipline", "focus"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q097",
    "text": "初心忘るべからず。",
    "author": "世阿弥",
    "category": ["discipline", "reflection"],
    "translated": true,
    "verification_status": "translated",
    "mood_tags": [],
    "season_tags": ["spring"],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q098",
    "text": "Don't let yesterday take up too much of today.",
    "author": "Will Rogers",
    "category": ["action", "focus"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["stressed"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "short",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q099",
    "text": "Live as if you were to die tomorrow. Learn as if you were to live forever.",
    "author": "Mahatma Gandhi",
    "category": ["action", "reflection"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "verified",
    "mood_tags": ["motivated", "brave"],
    "season_tags": [],
    "length": "medium",
    "enabled": true
  },
  {
    "id": "q100",
    "text": "Quietly endure. Silently suffer. Patiently wait.",
    "author": "",
    "category": ["endurance", "rest"],
    "translated": false,
    "verification_status": "original",
    "mood_tags": ["tired", "stressed"],
    "season_tags": ["winter"],
